<tag a="125" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />. <delay20 />Tieni!</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Che bel coordinato! <delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Il tuo stile sì che
è super, <delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />!<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Niente ti sta male. <delay20 />E con <tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x17 0xcd00 0xc 0x71 0x75 0x65 0x73 0x74 0x6f 0xc 0x71 0x75 0x65 0x73 0x74 0x61 0x0" /> <tag a="125" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />, farai ancora più faville, <delay8 />credimi!</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Si abbina alla grande al colore <tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x16 0xcd00 0x6 0x64 0x65 0x6c 0xa 0x64 0x65 0x6c 0x6c 0x61 0x0" />
<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x16 0xcd00 0x6 0x74 0x75 0x6f 0x6 0x74 0x75 0x61 0x0" /> <tag a="125" b="5" arg="0xcd00" />!</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Per me somiglia molto <tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x16 0xcd00 0xc 0x61 0x6c 0x20 0x74 0x75 0x6f 0x10 0x61 0x6c 0x6c 0x61 0x20 0x74 0x75 0x61 0x0" /> <tag a="125" b="5" arg="0xcd00" />! <delay20 />Insomma, <delay8 />ti starà benissimo!</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Vedrai che darà a te e <tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x16 0xcd00 0xc 0x61 0x6c 0x20 0x74 0x75 0x6f 0x10 0x61 0x6c 0x6c 0x61 0x20 0x74 0x75 0x61 0x0" /> <tag a="125" b="5" arg="0xcd00" /> <delay8 />un aspetto ancora più mitico!</message>
